ENTRY            F0253   20251211   20260305   20260305       F105
SUBENT        F0253001   20251211   20260305   20260305       F105
BIB                 11         25
TITLE      7Li+d -> 2alpha+n reaction
           Experimental results at Ed=1.0 MeV
AUTHOR     (V.D'Amico,G.Fazio,S.Jannelli,F.Mezzanares,R.Potenza)
INSTITUTE  (2ITYMES,2ITYLNS,2ITYCAT,2ITYSIC)
REFERENCE  (J,NC/A,22,313,1974)
FACILITY   (VDG,2ITYCAT) 2.7 MV
DETECTOR   (SIBAR) Two movable surface barrier detectors supplied
           by ORTEC. One of the detectors was fixed at an
           angle of 88.4 degr., while the second one was
           allowed to rotate between 30 and  110 degrees.
MONITOR    One of the detectors remained in a fixed position and
           acted also as a beam monitor.
SAMPLE     A natural Li target 0.5 mg/cm2 thick, evaporated on a
           polyvinilformal backing of 0.1 um was used.
METHOD     (BCINT,COINC,DSCAT)
ERR-ANALYS (ERR-SYS) Systematic error
           (DATA-ERR) No information about source of uncertainty
HISTORY    (20050523C)
           (20060414A) Reaction records were changed in subentries
           003,004,005. In sub3 FLAG was deleted and negative
           values of polar angle are given for the azimuth angle
           of 180 degrees.
           (20110225A) Error designations in sub 001-005 were
           changed.
           (20251211U) SD: Small corrections in all Subents.
ENDBIB              25
COMMON               2          3
EN         ERR-SYS
MEV        PER-CENT
  1.         15.
ENDCOMMON            3
ENDSUBENT           32
